  "system": {
    "description": "<p>This spell is like <em>prismatic sphere</em>, except the spell takes the form of a scintillating wall of colors that continually flow and shift into each other, creating a kaleidoscope effect. The wall's dimensions are 4 feet wide by 2 feet high per caster level. A <em>prismatic wall</em> materializing in a space occupied by a creature is disrupted and the spell is wasted. In all other respects but form, the spell acts as a <em>prismatic sphere</em>.</p>",
